OL,6,FPaul, who was a drummer for The Fall
OL,7,Ffrom 1980 to 1984, wrote the book to
OL,8,Fexamine Buzzcocks' influence on the
OL,9,Fhistory of Manchester music.
OL,11,FHe said: "He was a nice guy which
OL,12,Fsounds ridiculous but I think that's
OL,13,Fquite key. I think his nice guy-ness
OL,14,Fplayed into his music in a way that it
OL,15,Fdoesn't always with people in bands.
OL,17,F"It didn't distract, so it didn't make
OL,18,Fhim less charismatic because he was
OL,19,Fordinary, I think it made him more
OL,20,Fcharismatic in a way.
