OL,10,Fmade a thing of it, so it wasn't part
OL,11,Fof the act, he wasn't Elton John or
OL,12,F(David) Bowie, but then he didn't try
OL,13,Fto hide it either.
OL,15,F"He was walking to places in town and
OL,16,Fgetting the bus, and being quite open
OL,17,Fabout his sexuality, it was a
OL,18,Fparticularly brave thing to do.
